attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of furniture. They start by putting together the base frame, then the side bars. Next, they inspect the brackets and assemble the bottom tray. They screw the first bottom bracket, then disassemble the tray. Finally, they screw the left and right side bars, reassemble the bottom tray, and add the middle and top trays. They finish by attaching the four wheels.
